            <div type="translation" resp="part:reda">
                
                <p n="1">Hail! Prosperity!</p>
                <p n="1">
                    This glorious stone temple <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tirukkaṟṟaḷi</foreign></supplied> <supplied reason="subaudible">was constructed by/is named after</supplied> Vikrama Cōḻa. <note>The record does not unambuiguously specify if it is a temple that was constructed by Vikrama Cōḻa or whether it was erected in his honour. The translation, therefore, keeps the ambiguity of the original.</note>
                    
                </p>
                
            </div>
            
